-06-04T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:17:53.000Z","msg":"大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望"},{"pid":"5449634f3aa497057032e1d9e3808ab574c4b71a","tid":689102,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:19:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/六四-29周年-港大民研-逾三成港人認為無責任推動中國民主-比率創新高/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-29%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%2F&d=vzNaOYh9vM3wKlqSaL%2BMtkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0a9d7dfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B-29%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E6%AF%94%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%2F&h=ab607a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/六四-29周年-港大民研-逾三成港人認為無責任推動中國民主-比率創新高/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年是六四事件29週年，民研計劃公布自1993年每年均進行的六四週年調查。港大民研指出，宏觀而論，香港巿民的主流意見繼續認為中國政府當年處理不當、同情北京學生及支持平反六四。港大民研發現，大部分巿民繼續認為香港人有責任推動內地民主及經濟發展，<span style=\"color: red;\">而認為沒有責任推動中國民主發展的比率增至31%，再次錄得1993年有紀錄以來的新高。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec163a84cee2c73d0013b7f058692817bd3b9b11","tid":689102,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象</blockquote>大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要悼念，班大愛支係咪最應該為六四後仲支持民主回西路樓死先呢？？？尤其個班之後冚家攞定護照走既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"66e5ac6fbb330f086aeaf825695e0a2d4c041cfd","tid":689102,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52b802f94ae68527b2850f4a2deaabc66930f0b7","tid":689102,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f535ce1f9f3837de2fb0dec824b166c92fdfa4","tid":689102,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:17:53.000Z","msg":"大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"當年100萬人上街<br />\n其實唔少人係想推翻聯合聲明<br />\n唔想中國統治"},{"pid":"714d1f4496d986ff27c9d3d172f8db5fe71d0c7c","tid":689102,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港成班冚家挪住外國護照既大愛支，仲要班後生燒多幾多青春，去為一個一早燈紅酒綠紙醉金迷既遠方城市哭喪自瀆？？？</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>當年中國64<br />\n如果無香港人傷亡<br />\n香港駛唔駛年年攪咁多活動悼念<br />\n全球無一個地方好似香港大陣象</blockquote>大中華膠多 個時好多都對中國有幻想有希望</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要悼念，班大愛支係咪最應該為六四後仲支持民主回西路樓死先呢？？？尤其個班之後冚家攞定護照走既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im